text: Abominable (known as: Everest) s a computer animated movie made by DreamWorks Amimation, Pearl Studio. It stars the voices of Chloe Bennet, Albert Tsai, Tenzing Norgay Trainor, Eddie Izzard, Sarah Paulson, Tsai Chin, and Michelle Wong. ==References== Category:2019 computer-animated movies Category:Chinese movies Category:DreamWorks Animation movies Category:Movies set in China Category:Movies about Yeti
